message.body: Do you have any other contacts on map my run? Reason I ask is, I am curious to know if anyone ekse knows your workout regime as intimately as I do? It's great. Good job, your commitment is admirable.
I've got a few others. Would you prefer I leave it as private so as not to clog up your headlines? Only reason I record walks with the kids is to build points for rewards in Everymove
The running thing is still everyday though. Tonight was 298. Your kickboxing is pretty kickass, somewhat jealous.
I enjoy seeing it. It's motivating, figured I'd mention you were doing a great job. No sarcasm intended. The Muay Thai is great. You should come for a class
Maybe. Probably not for a few months though. Still settling in with the new job.
Lets catch up soon. Sunday I'm open
